{"tid":397953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最憎人問點解冇八達通　居澳港男論兩地矛盾","createTime":"2017-09-12T23:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T05:50:08.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"588fcd58b9c9507081056f0d3341844edb05d99c","tid":397953,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:59:52.000Z","msg":"「有一堆問題澳門人好憎：澳門有沒有電視看？為何澳門不可用八達通？你們年年都派錢嗎？」土生土長香港人，工程師Leo娶了澳門太太後，在澳門定居和工作四年多。年半前，他在Facebook開設專頁「港澳小不同」，以輕鬆手法畫出兩地生活上的差異和軼事。自言不理解澳門「加強版蛇齋餅糉」的他，提到即將舉行的立法會選舉：「澳門人看重民生，風災後基本不會改變市民訴求，因為選舉機制不民主，議席上建制『屈曬機』。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：蘇汝卿　攝影：袁志中　剪接：魏利民<br />\n<br />\n「做議員最簡單應該係要得到XX同鄉會，X聯XX會支持，就好似你咁弱智嘅人都選到。」Leo畫的卡通，不時出現澳門人妻子，解答港人身分的他對澳門的疑惑。「其實香港人對澳門誤解較大，很多人來到澳門，覺得理所當然可用香港一套，其實澳門很多方面有自己的文化。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有骨氣vs冇骨氣？</strong><br />\n<br />\n8月23日颱風「天鴿」吹襲，造成澳門過百人受傷，十人死亡，亦暴露了賭城的基建千瘡百孔，「最氣的不就是曾志豪寫『你們年年派錢，那些是帛金。』，有人說『你們搞到要出解放軍，冇骨氣，抵食！』」澳門網民要求他們道歉，更有澳門的士在車窗貼上：「港燦與狗」不得上車。對於「冇骨氣」之說，Leo回應指澳門回歸前，葡國「hea做」；回歸後澳門人又長期面對無能的特區政府，所以對「阿爺」沒甚麼反感，亦有人真心感激解放軍。對澳門政府已不能更失望，「這次很憤怒，但只限網上世界，大家不斷罵太遲才掛八號波。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>李氏力場vs澳門賭「牆」</strong><br />\n<br />\nLeo指澳門盛傳有一度更強的力場阻止颱風信號懸掛，以確保賭博和旅遊業不受影響：「一堵強大的『賭牆』擋住了。大家都說政府收了賭場錢，因為賭場大多在早上八時交更，九時才掛八號風球，打工仔不就全都要上班。」香港每年平均三至四個八號風球，而相隔只六十公里的澳門，三年來竟只掛了一次八號風球，2004年更取消了紅雨黑雨警告信號。「一直有海水倒灌問題，澳門政府從未打算解決。災後有何措施？派錢。但派錢有何用？」與其靠政府、靠官媒，澳門民間自救，當晚這位工程師畫了一張防海水倒灌設計圖：將現有的疏洞鐵圍欄轉為石屎。Leo希望拋磚引玉，讓網民一起想出長遠解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>滿街義工　民間自救</strong><br />\n<br />\n而Leo最感動的是災後整條街都是義工：「三四天沒有電，十層大廈不能用電梯，住了很多老人，幾百人輪流搬水、搬飯。」而不少港人也低調救災：「他們來到沒有車，唯有伸手截車去問，真的有澳門人願意載他們，而且是連續幾天載到不同區。」一些香港義工特地到舊區：「災後三四天了，那些公公婆婆說：『你們是第一批義工來派飯。』」Leo看到線下的澳門，不少港澳人合力救災：「香港和澳門本來就是姊妹城市，我覺得最好是大家明白澳門和香港有少少區別。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170912/large/1505217120_e66f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170912%2Flarge%2F1505217120_e66f.jpg&h=04451183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170912/large/1505217121_5d0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170912%2Flarge%2F1505217121_5d0c.jpg&h=277634b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLeo畫的卡通，不時出現澳門人妻子，解答港人身分的他對澳門的疑惑。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170912/large/1505217123_f7cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170912%2Flarge%2F1505217123_f7cb.jpg&h=73207ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與其靠政府、靠官媒，澳門民間自救，風災當晚這位工程師畫了一張防海水倒灌設計圖：將現有的疏洞鐵圍欄轉為石屎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57201987&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57201987%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170913&d=Bv%2BXv7YOYnV%2FD5Ad20%2Fb4iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c0598a9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57201987%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170913&h=5685ed7b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57201987&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170913</a>"},{"pid":"da4b7fcd6afdf130d3f71f169275fb8ff33b964c","tid":397953,"uid":29314,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:06:45.000Z","msg":"鄰國既事"},{"pid":"0cf1086dec6ccd43af83cd3f769c428e7bcd8d16","tid":397953,"uid":26156,"like":30,"dislike":5,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:12:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a3f1bbade067032d10cc19c5c22770ef8fc04cf","tid":397953,"uid":106320,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4字總結<br />\n<br />\n澳門好垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecce3ff4f482f8a654edcf4c6d61c7f3b3e532c","tid":397953,"uid":127569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:16:32.000Z","msg":"澳門wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c065292e1224e40fbb7592efb5eb5ecf426758","tid":397953,"uid":66811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:21:54.000Z","msg":"小島風情比暴發戶搞到咁"},{"pid":"28c1189a2b2a4e3d2b51c9c1a07b9817174c9fd5","tid":397953,"uid":1377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:23:01.000Z","msg":"唔想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cad545faca28c07d1ba6bbadf703f19eac3fa52","tid":397953,"uid":39365,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:23:01.000Z","msg":"Leo回應指澳門回歸前，葡國「hea做」；回歸後澳門人又長期面對無能的特區政府，所以對「阿爺」沒甚麼反感，亦有人真心感激解放軍<br />\n<br />\n係唔係好矛盾? 定係斯德哥爾摩症後群?"},{"pid":"3d35555e952b2f0dcca8a621f07398376cdfef52","tid":397953,"uid":41245,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:23:15.000Z","msg":"澳門人唔係又係以為自己一樣有「特別行政區」就可以同香港人扮熟嘛？<br />\n香港本身都好多香港人不滿<br />\n澳門仲要次一等走出嚟刷存在感？<br />\n你係有骨氣嘅，fine、但你地唔係喎<br />\n唔好話香港人睇唔起澳門，香港人連冇骨氣嘅香港人都睇唔起，根本一視同仁，港豬澳豬都係垃圾，只係澳門出親嚟「反駁」嘅都係澳豬，一啲啲反抗意識都冇，你叫香港人仲可以畀咩反應你？keep on呀叫你地？<br />\n文化差異呀，你地澳門人都係少啲出嚟啦"},{"pid":"42a123487f5f9f2bac33cb189030f54b376c078e","tid":397953,"uid":53037,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:26:52.000Z","msg":"又想靠畫埋啲核突公仔上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3da133ec68d7221c6a8b75958abdb2970aed56f","tid":397953,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Leo回應指澳門回歸前，葡國「hea做」；回歸後澳門人又長期面對無能的特區政府，所以對「阿爺」沒甚麼反感，亦有人真心感激解放軍<br />\n<br />\n係唔係好矛盾? 定係斯德哥爾摩症後群?</blockquote><br />\n澳門人就係有依個特性，ip都唔洗check<br />\n佢地好識為佢地親中嘅行為搵原因<br />\n而依啲係基於同支那各城市一樣，冇咩思想<br />\n文化唔同"},{"pid":"06700590667ade545f9582b819890e52c1bf8132","tid":397953,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:32:17.000Z","msg":"on9。文化有優劣之分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a73592d5bb1180d5e3603dbdc3cfe5a5fe9ccec","tid":397953,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:32:47.000Z","msg":"澳門有冇討論區？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd22a174a34db6cb18383f3b3f6ba10e2f7c7d10","tid":397953,"uid":52276,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:34:53.000Z","msg":"居澳港男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌我一睇以為係澳洲，原來係中國澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bf8f21cfedfe3474d0a99324841a4418cfd20a","tid":397953,"uid":27458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:36:14.000Z","msg":"澳門點解無八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8924547188d181bc87024c6385ad97108dfec3","tid":397953,"uid":3239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Leo回應指澳門回歸前，葡國「hea做」；回歸後澳門人又長期面對無能的特區政府，所以對「阿爺」沒甚麼反感，亦有人真心感激解放軍<br />\n<br />\n係唔係好矛盾? 定係斯德哥爾摩症後群?</blockquote><br />\nload 左一陣先明<br />\n真係癡撚線"},{"pid":"28f2ade91e5e5f4ca6072afe48c288960926c2ab","tid":397953,"uid":2521,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:42:02.000Z","msg":"其實澳門人咁諗係錯唔晒<br />\n不過澳門係由黑暗時代升封建時代<br />\n香港係由帝皇時代倒退返封建<br />\n感覺當然差好多"},{"pid":"6d42d692a88081bd675575f7eb37c374ada6170e","tid":397953,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:18:58.000Z","msg":"澳門無八達通？綠色嗰張乜鳩黎？<br />\n澳門搭賭場車又唔洗錢，我都想香港有馬會車"},{"pid":"95c28726e3e8d626669806e3b91ee75f694b4cf9","tid":397953,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又想靠畫埋啲核突公仔上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n魚生啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02391b10f57f957b46b0b4c054281bc9ad4c8751","tid":397953,"uid":61463,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:33:00.000Z","msg":"姊你老母妹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又扮熟"},{"pid":"6db03562e46eb12ea0ee47252583ab1221db1197","tid":397953,"uid":9887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"澳門政府無能會唔關阿爺事？智商係咪咁低呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a134153d709e38e4ff1b5d39813b52b64e2d64","tid":397953,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Leo回應指澳門回歸前，葡國「hea做」；回歸後澳門人又長期面對無能的特區政府，所以對「阿爺」沒甚麼反感，亦有人真心感激解放軍<br />\n<br />\n係唔係好矛盾? 定係斯德哥爾摩症後群?</blockquote><br />\n權力崇拜"},{"pid":"049b1974b4b4177423a4d2820ef2475afe91243b","tid":397953,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"剩係睇個立法會有一班立法會議員係有特首直接委任就知啦, <br />\n講前景, 澳門收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔關澳門平民事, 因為同香港人一樣, 好多野企撚埋出黎都改變唔到, <br />\n任由宰割"},{"pid":"62c0a98fc2a2651d3ae4a098b0c23b1dc8d8965c","tid":397953,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5defedcfb2e882bc6a1be567ce2900852b5a9320","tid":397953,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門政府無能會唔關阿爺事？智商係咪咁低呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢哋仲信緊只有貪官，沒有暴君嗰套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}